name: Duwap Kaine
description: '''Donald George Ruffin''' (born February 21, 2002), known professionally as '''Duwap Kaine''' is an American rapper, singer, and songwriter from [[Savannah, Georgia]]. He is known for his projects ''Underdog'' and ''Bad Kid from the 4'', as well as his early collaborations with record producer [[Pi'erre Bourne]].
